# Cloudflare Pages Redirects
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# 支持无 .html 后缀的清洁 URL（301 永久重定向，保证资源路径正确）

/index          /index.html       301
/courses        /courses.html     301
/course         /course.html      301
/search         /search.html      301
/statistics     /statistics.html  301
/about          /about.html       301
/faq            /faq.html         301
/new-review     /new-review.html  301

# 课程详情短链接
/course/:sqid   /course.html?sqid=:sqid   301
